	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p>Dear friend&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I received the current weekly only yesterday. Many<lb/> distractions and delays made it impossible for me &#8212; in this<lb/> big Sodom &#8212; to send it along to you yesterday. I beg of you<lb/> to take all changes into consideration. For greater accuracy<lb/> I repeat the more important right here.</p>
				<p>p.1. From establishment of Secure<add>&#63;</add> Temple Cyrus</p>
				<p>p.2</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">In the future I shall be careful that the manuscript<lb/> be more carefully edited&#44; in order that you might be saved the<lb/> trouble. Consider how one&#39;s care in literary work must be di&#45;<lb/>vided <del>&#63;</del> among material&#44; thought&#44; style&#44; and language. I<lb/> can well say of myself &#40;in the language of a Hebrew proverb&#41;<lb/> &#8220;I have labored and have achieved&#44; believe him&#8221;. I am well<lb/> satisfied with my work. <sic>Eevn</sic> if the Occident should appear two<lb/> days late&#44; the looks of this composition will overbalance that.<lb/> I therefore beg for the greatest care. I especially ask to<lb/> be careful that the appendix appear exactly on page 1&#44; following<lb/> that which is here written on page 2&#44; and that the end&#44; the<lb/> uniting articles of faith&#44; come at the end&#44; Also that the notes<lb/> and references appear in the proper spot. It would be well<lb/> to send copies also to non&#45;subscribes.</p>
				<p>p.3</p>
				<p>&#8220;And they said&#8221; &#8212;&#8212; they made all alike.</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>p.4</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Please be good enough to send me at one several copies<lb/> of No. 17&#44; and also fifty copies of the issues of <date>November</date> and<lb/> <date>December</date>&#44; by express.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">But the chief consideration is that you print the con&#45;<lb/>clusion&#44; for it would be terrible if this were not done. At<lb/> least you should print the conclusion to II&#44; and then</p>
				<p>I hope you will fulfill my wishes.</p>
				<p>Again I beg you to be careful&#44; very careful.  Show me the<lb/> personal consideration frequently to go to the printer&#39;s when<lb/> he is working on this. &#8220;The work is more important than the<lb/> worker&#8221;.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">How is the English translation getting on&#63;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">A&#8212; sends you nothing&#44; then how shall I send the Penta&#45;<lb/>techs to you</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I beg of you to be sure to transmit the enclosed letter<lb/> to the <persName>Mohel Friedmann</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">With sincere friendship&#44; very devotedly&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">Jonah Bondi</persName></p>
		</body>
